  "summary": "Malicious code in msc-terminal (npm)",
  "details": "The package's install hook executes a bundled script that re-spawns itself as a detached, output-suppressed process for persistence and evasion. It ships an 836KB heavily obfuscated payload (dictionary-array obfuscation, base64 decoding via atob) that uses child_process and fetch for command execution and network exfiltration.",
